Lekin, liberal arts education kai faide rakhti hai aur zindagi mein aap ko aik edge de sakti hai. Liberal arts education aap ko woh skills, ilm, aur tajurba deti hai jo aap ko apni poori salahiyat tak pohanchne aur aik kamyab, maqsad bhari mustaqbil banane mein madadgar sabit hoti hai.

Liberal arts curriculum mein “one size fits all” ka tareeqa nahi hota; balkeh aap khud sochna, masail ka tajziya karna, aur hal nikalna seekhte hain. Yeh qeemti tajurba kisi bhi career mein aap ke liye faida mand hai, kyun ke aap behtar faislay kar sakte hain, mushkil masail hal kar sakte hain, aur apne gird o nawahi ki duniya ko samajh sakte hain.

Liberal arts education aap ko mukhtalif topics explore karne ka mauka bhi deti hai, jis se aap ko aik well-rounded education milti hai. Jab aap mukhtalif topics se waqif hote hain, to aap patterns pehchan sakte hain, mukhtalif topics ke darmiyan connections bana sakte hain, aur duniya ko aik naya nazariya se dekh sakte hain.

Akhir mein, liberal arts education aap ko apne peers ke sath kaam karne aur seekhne ka bhi mauka deti hai. Discussions, debates, aur constructive criticism ke zariye, aap dusre students se seekhte hain jo mukhtalif backgrounds, beliefs, aur perspectives rakhte hain. Yeh tajurba aap ka worldview barhata hai, aap ki communication aur interpersonal skills behtar banata hai, aur aap ko global issues ko samajhne mein madad karta hai.

Liberal arts education be qeemat hai aur usay un logon ki baton mein dabna nahi chahiye jo kehte hain ke yeh guzishta zamane ki baat hai. Yeh aap ko woh skills aur ilm deti hai jo mukhtalif fields mein kamyabi ke liye zaroori hain aur aise tajurbe deti hai jo zindagi bhar kaam aate hain. Chahe aap sciences, humanities, ya arts mein career banayein, liberal arts education aap ko woh advantage de sakti hai jo aap ko apni poori salahiyat tak pohanchne mein madad karegi.

    for i in range(len(string1)):

    for i in range(len(string2)):

    # Agar koi frequency negative ho jaye,
